{"tid":528451,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好掛住huge","createTime":"2018-01-13T19:06:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-16T16:47:38.000Z","uid":52230,"like":19,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e7cf5a2bbf47c9e6ae050c5c976f36381e3c71e5","tid":528451,"uid":52230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T19:06:40.000Z","msg":"Huge係12月31日因為facebook不足70000likes未能達成目標而收皮<br />\n<br />\n懶人包：事發原因基於一個新建Facebook page 抄襲huge原創題材而暴升40000likes 而原創嘅huge page同呢個page所抄襲而得到嘅成就相差極大而對觀眾反應感到失望最終決定目標於2017年12月31日如果Facebook page不足70000likes從始停止運作 而最終huge最後亦事與願違地以50000likes嘅成果下宣布告終<br />\n<br />\nHuge喺大約一年前開live正式宣布呢個決定 提及對於香港觀眾反應冷淡而失望 表示認為香港人不尊重原創 大部分page以抄襲方式而紅 即使知道但依然冇任何表示 放縱抄襲行為 導致香港嘅原創越黎越少 <br />\n<br />\n而huge最終亦成為香港依個風氣下嘅犧牲品 雖然huge唔係好出名 YouTube subscribe 亦唔夠20000 但佢地嘅原創性 質素同埋用心都非常值得尊重 由佢地嘅prank同小品等等 好睇得出佢地好用心製作 亦好享受製作 一直以黎為觀眾帶黎歡樂 我亦好感激佢地一直以黎嘅付出 雖然huge已經成為歷史 但佢地成為歷史嘅原因非常值得香港人關注 香港充斥太多抄襲嘅kol 我希望就算喺huge嘅haters 都先唔好評論對於huge呢個決定同結局嘅對錯 就佢地嘅結局為鑑 好好了解下香港人嘅呢個風氣 我雖然唔敢講我有盡哂責任 因為我曾經都喺負責食花生唔幫手嘅一份子 但我希望huge就算收左皮 但呢個結果都可以改變到香港呢個唔公平 侵犯創作權嘅風氣 各位連登嘅正義之士 點解連登咁多屌柒人抄啲post但呢啲kol e.g. 大大與小妹 一個都未消失？ 我好希望大家可以齊心 幫手檢舉呢啲page 就算唔喺huge嘅fans 冇睇開佢地 haters cd-rom 都好都希望你地幫手 亦希望呢個喺身為花生觀眾可以為佢地做嘅最後一件事<br />\n<br />\n最後希望huge友誼永固 多謝你地<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/14/025813_1e542e53292d194678070162f8edde27.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F14%2F025813_1e542e53292d194678070162f8edde27.jpeg&h=7994d288&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nHuge Facebook page <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HUGEHK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHUGEHK%2F&d=JmjKm%2FXIeRW2n9jwsKbyyv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=88b1323c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HUGEHK/</a><br />\nHuge YouTube <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCkfW7xN8QyLU7crYaKCTT1w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCkfW7xN8QyLU7crYaKCTT1w&d=JmjKm%2FXIeRW2n9jwsKbyyv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=38825ffe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCkfW7xN8QyLU7crYaKCTT1w</a><br />\nHuge instagram<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/hu.ge.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fhu.ge.hk&d=JmjKm%2FXIeRW2n9jwsKbyyv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=b2bbf744\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.instagram.com/hu.ge.hk</a><br />\n直播原link<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HUGEHK/videos/982454311854396/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHUGEHK%2Fvideos%2F982454311854396%2F&d=JmjKm%2FXIeRW2n9jwsKbyyv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=da3f79b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HUGEHK/videos/982454311854396/</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然huge收左皮 但有心嘅都上去睇下佢地嘅片 like subscribe 同 share!"},{"pid":"e57afc51996c56a36a11c1ae3a0d2f536fbd6713","tid":528451,"uid":10820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T19:50:47.000Z","msg":"邊個fb page抄佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f54c4fd5cd8d9523466709b809abbba4d02f5176","tid":528451,"uid":6803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T21:35:30.000Z","msg":"想知咩事分開左兩邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdaead1f3da3b5211dc6fff6c96e22de0b74254d","tid":528451,"uid":34069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T21:36:52.000Z","msg":"想知佢地係咪嘈左? 咩事?"},{"pid":"60d2be2451c99ed04f92d69718f804196254745f","tid":528451,"uid":52230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e57afc51996c56a36a11c1ae3a0d2f536fbd6713","tid":528451,"uid":10820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T19:50:47.000Z","msg":"邊個fb page抄佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=